<div id="review_385682927" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/385682927" />
    <a title="Rameez Rahman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7518474-rameez-rahman"><img alt="Rameez Rahman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1577961298p2/7518474.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/385682927?book_show_action=true">Aug 06, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rameez Rahman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rameez Rahman" href="/user/show/7518474-rameez-rahman">Rameez Rahman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7518474-rameez-rahman?shelf=malayalam">malayalam</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer385682927" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2870352298916208563">Ever happened to you that you picked up a book to read in your bed and spent the first few hours of the night reading it in one go and spending the rest thinking about it? That&apos;s what this book did to me.<br/><br/>One of the most hard hitting books in Malayalam that I have read recently. I haven&apos;t read any other works of Benyamin (yet) and so I dont know if its his style of writing, but what stood out was the simplicity so befitting the narrator in the language being used for telling the story, and all th</span>
  <span id="freeText2870352298916208563" style="display:none">Ever happened to you that you picked up a book to read in your bed and spent the first few hours of the night reading it in one go and spending the rest thinking about it? That's what this book did to me.<br /><br />One of the most hard hitting books in Malayalam that I have read recently. I haven't read any other works of Benyamin (yet) and so I dont know if its his style of writing, but what stood out was the simplicity so befitting the narrator in the language being used for telling the story, and all the while I couldnt think that anyone other than Najeeb himself could had written this.<br /><br />The more I read the less reasons I found to crib about my life. <br />Amazing tale of human perseverance, hope and belief. Highly recommended.<br /><br /> </span>
  <a data-text-id="2870352298916208563" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


