<li class='cover' id='bookCover_10583033'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10583033-oru-sangeerthanam-pole"><img alt="ഒരു സങ്കീര്‍ത്തനം പോലെ [Oru Sangeerthanam Pole]" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1298546887l/10583033._SX98_.jpg" />
